effect:
Choose a Size 1 _Earthen_ _Obstacle_ within Range. Move it to an adjacent, unoccupied space, then become _Charging_. While _Charging_, the _Obstacle_ gains 1 _Guard_ and may not be moved by another creature. At the end of each _Phase_, including the current one, you may either fire the _Obstacle_ or continue _Charging_.
&nbsp;
If you continue _Charging_, you may _Pull_ 1 the _Obstacle_.
&nbsp;
If you fire the _Obstacle_, attack with the below profile in a _Line_ 4+X, where X is the number of _Phases_ you've been _Charging_, not including the initial _Phase_ where you began the effect. Place the _Obstacle_ at the end of the _Area_, or the nearest unoccupied space, prioritizing those in the _Area_.
&nbsp;
If the _Obstacle_ is destroyed, end this effect.
